---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Article from "../components/Article.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import hikeImage from "/src/assets/images/hike_image.svg";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="flex">
    <Image
      src={hikeImage}
      alt="hiking person"
      decoding="async"
      loading="eager"
      width="256"
      height="256"
      class="image-hike"
    />
  </div>

  <Article id="about" title="About Me">
    <p>
      Hello! I'm Jaromir, a frontend developer specializing in Angular. I thrive
      on bringing innovative ideas to life on the web. Over the past few years,
      I've honed my skills in Angular, becoming proficient in building dynamic
      and responsive applications.
    </p>

    <p>
      Currently, I'm on my dream hiking trip in the beautiful landscapes of
      Sweden. This adventure is not just a break from my usual coding routine
      but also a source of inspiration. The serene environment and the
      challenges of hiking mirror my approach to development â€“ always exploring,
      learning, and pushing my limits.
    </p>

    <p>Feel free to contact me.</p>
  </Article>
  <Article id="skills" title="Skills">
    <div class="text-center">
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of angular"
        loading="eager"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/angular/angular-original.svg"
      />
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of typescript"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg"
      />
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of css"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"
      />
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of html"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"
      />
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of ngrx"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/ngrx/ngrx-original.svg"
      />
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of ionic  "
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/ionic/ionic-original.svg"
      />
      <Image
        width="60"
        height="60"
        loading="eager"
        class="skill-button"
        alt="logo of git"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"
      />
    </div>
  </Article>
  <Article id="blogs" title="Interests">
    <p>
      When I'm not coding or hiking, you'll find me diving into new
      technologies, playing video games, board games, or enjoying a good book.
      My goal is to continue growing as a developer and to contribute to
      projects that make a positive impact.
    </p>
  </Article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .image-hike {
    object-fit: cover;
    margin: auto;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .flex {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .text-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .skill-button {
    margin: 0.5rem;
    height: 4rem;
    width: 4rem;
  }
</style>
